embeds.title: Welcome!
embeds.description:
It's great to see you! :3
I'm here to get you started with how we do things around here.

1. **Please make sure to be respectful.** Agree to disagree.
    a. **Bigotry will not be tolerated.**
2. **Follow [Discord's Terms of Service](https://discord.com/terms).** You must be over the age of 13 years of age to use Discord.
3. **Please refrain from saying slurs.** All slurs go through our slur policy. (read more below)
4. **Please stick to English.** To make moderation easier, we ask you to speak in the English language.
5. **Make sure you use common sense.** Just because it isn't listed here, doesn't mean you can't get punished for it.

Slurs can be harmful. So we ask that you stick to these guidelines to keep the community safe:
* Don't use slurs in a harmful manner. (ex. "You're such a \*\*\*!")
* Try to keep slurs in spoilers. (how 2 spoiler: `||spoiler||`)
* Keep in mind that even if you follow these guidelines, you may be punished for using slurs.
